The command-line interface for Stocksmith

  $ stocksmith help <command>                     Display help for a command
  $ stocksmith account                            Show account information
  $ stocksmith api <METHOD> <path>                Make authenticated API requests
  $ stocksmith auth login | status | logout       Authenticate with Stocksmith
  $ stocksmith materials list | show              Manage materials
  $ stocksmith products list | show               Manage products
  $ stocksmith components list | show             Manage components
  $ stocksmith manufactures list | show           Manage manufactures
  $ stocksmith recipes list | show                Manage recipes
  $ stocksmith expenses list | show               Manage expenses
  $ stocksmith completion <shell>                 Generate shell completion scripts
  $ stocksmith version                            Print version information
  $ stocksmith update                             Update stocksmith to the latest release

Flags:
      --json           Output raw API envelope (pretty-printed JSON)
      --ndjson         Output auto-paginated NDJSON stream
      --token <token>  API token (overrides stored credentials)
      --api-url <url>  API base URL
      --no-color       Disable ANSI color output
      --verbose        Show HTTP request/response detail (token redacted)
  -h, --help           Show help for a command

Environment Variables:
  STOCKSMITH_API_TOKEN  API token used for requests (CI, scripts)
  STOCKSMITH_API_URL    API base URL override
  NO_COLOR              Disable colored output (no-color.org convention)

try: stocksmith materials list

Learn more at https://cli.stocksmith.dev/getting-started
